These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
House: wooden, cape-cod, victorian, palace, farmhouse, cottage, tower
1. the cottage house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
2. the wooden house is on the left of the palace house##1
3. the tower house is on the left of the victorian house##1
4. the farmhouse house is between the wooden house and the victorian house##2
5. the palace house is between the cape-cod house and the wooden house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| House   | tower | victorian | farmhouse | wooden | palace | cape-cod | cottage |

