.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: daisy, begonia, azalea, orchid, sunflower, balloon-flower, amaryllis
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
4. the person who growsazalea is between the person who growsorchid and the person who growsdaisy##2
5. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the person who growsazalea is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | amaryllis | daisy | azalea | orchid | begonia | sunflower |

