.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: magic-tricks, sudoku, woodworking, puzzles, rock-climbing, baking, reading
1. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |      4       |   5   |     6     |   7    |
| Hobby   | reading | puzzles | baking | rock-climbing | woodworking | sudoku | magic-tricks |

