.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-12::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: september, october, may, february, march, january, august
1. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in february##2
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |  3  |    4     |  5  |    6    |   7    |
| Birthday   | march | may | august | february | september | january | october |

