6. the fan dubstep is on the right of the fan blues##1
7. the fan indie is on the left of the fan reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3  |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Music-Genre   | disco | house | d&b | indie | reggae | blues | dubstep |

